        {
            "id": 6085568,
            "title": "盤中速報 - Palo Alto Networks Inc(PANW-US)大跌5.02%，報173.85美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Palo Alto Networks Inc(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:PANW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/PANW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">PANW-US</a>)截至台北時間31日22:43股價下跌9.18美元，報173.85美元，跌幅5.02%，成交量8,846,698（股），盤中最高價183.82美元、最低價173.85美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.11%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.51%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.88%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-1.6%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>Palo Alto Networks Inc(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:PANW:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/PANW\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">PANW-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-6.96%</li> <li>近 1 月：-10.56%</li> <li>近 3 月：-2.09%</li> <li>近 6 月：-2.34%</li> <li>今年以來：+0.59%</li></ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6085568",
